'''Buffalo Creek''' is a [[tributary]] of the [[West Branch Susquehanna River]] in  [[Union County, Pennsylvania|Union County]], [[Pennsylvania]] in the [[United States]].

Buffalo Creek joins the West Branch Susquehanna River at the borough of [[Lewisburg, Pennsylvania|Lewisburg]].

